import { Container, Row, Col, Tab, Nav } from "react-bootstrap"; import colorSharp2 from "../assets/img/color-sharp2.png"; import 'animate.css'; import "./Experience.css"; import TrackVisibility from 'react-on-screen'; import { useEffect } from 'react'; export const Experience = () => { useEffect(() => { function isElementInViewport(el) { const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect(); return ( rect.top >= 0 && rect.left >= 0 && rect.bottom <= (window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight) ); } function checkVisibility() { const experienceSection = document.querySelector('.experience'); const experienceItems = document.querySelectorAll('.experience-item'); if (isElementInViewport(experienceSection)) { experienceItems.forEach((item) => { if (isElementInViewport(item)) { item.classList.add('show'); } }); } } window.addEventListener('scroll', checkVisibility); return () => { window.removeEventListener('scroll', checkVisibility); }; }, []); return (

  • Executed the design of a logo for the IT department, contributing to the department's visual identity.

Duration: July 2022 – August 2022

Location: 4 WTC, NY

  • Assisted with database development using SQL, created Web Forms using HTML, CSS.
